Rating: 3
Moist, tasty cake and very easy to make! Substituted 1/2 tsp each ginger, allspice, cloves, 1/4 tsp nutmeg, 3/4 tsp cinnamon, for the pumpkin pie spice. Baking time was under 45 minutes.

